Checkbox.name: Checkbox
example:
<script>
	    const demos = [
	        {
	            title: '',
	            desc: '',
	            code: `
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="1" checked/>
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="2" />`
	        },
	        {
	            title: '',
	            desc: 'disabled',
	            code: `
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="3" disabled />
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="4" disabled />`
	        },
	        {
	            title: 'change',
	            desc: '',
	            code: `
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="1"  @change="handleChange" :checked="selected.indexOf('1') != -1"/>
	                        <sw-checkbox label=""  value="2"  @change="handleChange"/>`,
	            options: {
	                data(){
	                    return {
	                        selected: ['1']
	                    }
	                },
	                methods: {
	                    handleChange(val){
	                        let index = this.selected.indexOf(val)
	                        if(index === -1){
	                            this.selected.push(val)
	                        }else{
	                            this.selected.splice(index,1)
	                        }
	                        alert(this.selected)
	                    }
	                }
	            }
	        }
	    ]
	    import Base from '../base.vue'
	    export default {
	        name: 'PageCheckbox',
	        extends:Base,
	        data(){
	            return {
	                demos: demos
	            }
	        }
	    }
	</script>
